snippet.title: Bicycle Solitaire gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Bicycle Solitaire, Dos PC game produced by SWFTE International in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/bicycle-solitaire/4774/
Trying out a couple of different variations on solitaire in this card game collection.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
